IN a Twitter stunt that has left critics stunned, US President Donald Trump posted a video of himself yesterday tackling &ldquo;CNN&rdquo;.The TV news outlet has been critical of Trump and his presidency, and has repeatedly been attacked by him. He often labels their content &ldquo;fake news&rdquo;. He has previously described mainstream press as "the enemies of the people". Defenders of free press have reacted with horror, saying that this was actually an attack on democracy by the controversial president. They also worry it will encourage his supporters to become physically violent with journalists.#FraudNewsCNN #FNN pic.twitter.com/WYUnHjjUjg&mdash; Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) July 2, 2017